'''Claudette Mukasakindi''' (yavutse 25 Ukuboza 1982 i Nyarugenge ) ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwandakazi]] ni umukinnyi ukora amasiganwa wiruka intera ndende . <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20120723000720/http://www.london2012.com/athlete/mukasakindi-claudette-1091094/</ref> Yarushanwe muri marato mu mikino Olempike ya 2012, aza ku mwanya wa 101 akoresha amasaha 2:51:07. <ref>https://archive.today/20121205100448/www.london2012.com/athletics/event/women-marathon/index.html?v=20120806-055117400</ref> Mu mikino ya Commonwealth 2014, yarangije ku mwanya wa 11 muri metero 10000 mu bagore. <ref>http://g2014results.thecgf.com/athlete/athletics/1035212/claudette_mukasakindi.html</ref> Yahataniraga u [[Rwanda]] mu mikino Olempike ya 2016 muri marato y'abagore. Yabaye uwa 126 hamwe nigihe cya 3: 05.57. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20160826085412/https://www.rio2016.com/en/athletics-standings-at-womens-marathon</ref> Yabaye uwatwaye ibendera ry'u [[Rwanda]] mu birori byo gusoza. <ref>https://www.olympic.org/news/the-flagbearers-for-the-rio-2016-closing-ceremony</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mukasakindi yagize umwaka mwiza muri 2012, atwara Cagliari Marathon muri Gicurasi, hamwe nigihe cyiza cya 2:40:18. <ref>http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2012-05-08/52571/</ref> Iyi mikorere yari mu gihe cyasabwaga na IAAF kugira ngo ijye mu majonjora y'imikino Olempike ya 2012, ariko icyifuzo cya Mukasakindi cyo kwitabira iyo mikino cyabanje kwangwa kubera ko ibirori bya Cagliari bitari irushanwa ryujuje ibyangombwa. <ref>http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2012-05-17/52915/</ref> Mu kurangiza ariko, yemerewe kwiruka, arangiza ku mwanya wa 101 mubirori, hamwe nigihe cya 2:51:07. <ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/olympics/2012/athletes/f4cbd665-1449-4db8-b941-d90a68871237</ref>

Mu mikino Olempike ya 2016 yabereye i [[Rio de Janeiro]], Mukasakindi yongeye kwitabira marato y'abagore, umwe mu Banyarwanda barindwi bahatanira iyo mikino. <ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20160927213022/https://www.rio2016.com/en/rwanda</ref> Yizeraga ko azanoza imikorere ye i Londres, kandi yamaze igihe kinini yitegura muri [[Kenya]] no mu [[Ubutaliyani|Butaliyani]], ndetse no mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref>http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2016-08-14/202583/</ref> Nubwo aya mahugurwa, imikorere ye muri ibyo birori yari mibi. Mukasakindi yarangije ku mwanya wa 126 muri iryo siganwa, avuye kuri133, anashyiraho igihe cya 3:05:57. <ref name="AnkleInjury">http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/article/2016-08-16/202639/</ref> Yavuze ko ibisubizo byatewe n’imvune yo mu kaguru yagize mu myitozo, hasigaye iminsi itatu ngo ibyo birori bitangire; ntabwo yari yarigeze atekereza ko ari ikibazo mbere yo gusiganwa, ariko akaguru katangiye kumutera ibibazo kuri  21 kilometres (13 mi) mu isiganwa, bikomera nyuma ya 25 kilometres (16 mi) . <ref name="AnkleInjury" /> Yakomeje kugeza  isiganwa rirangiye, ariko yavuze ko imvune ari yo mpamvu nyamukuru yamuteye kwitwara nabi. <ref name="AnkleInjury" />

